lines: 1. Jathieth maduong` osudo ka,En Yesu ma Jakonywa;Wachne omiyo chunya mor,Yaye, winjuru dwonde.
Wer mamit mar jopolo,Ka gipako Ruoth Yesu,Nying` moloyo nying` duto,Yesu kende, Yesu.
2. Oseweyoni richoni,Winji Yesu kowacho;Chunyi koro obed gi kuwe,Kichiko wang` yor polo.
3. Wadend Nyarombono motho;Koro ayie kuom Yesu.Ahero nying` mar Jawarna,Ahero nying`no, Yesu.
4. Nying`no ogolo richona,Onge maromo kode;Chunya mor nade kawinjoNying`no maber mar Yesu.
5. Koduogo chiwo osimbo,Osimb ngima mar lochoEka wanabedi bute,Wanadend Jawar Yesu.
